1,"uid":130320,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T13:09:20.000Z","msg":"用戶名明明係男人"},{"pid":"6d687f6f5e4b82af2640b8fa43d0180ccc8a745c","tid":2445221,"uid":48901,"like":64,"dislike":0,"score":64,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T13:11:40.000Z","msg":"先唔講屋企係藍先<br />\n淨係脾氣暴躁已經飛得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家都咁，結左婚仲唔打到你飛天呀？"},{"pid":"635318a33ead301fe6080afe3846649f3513988e","tid":2445221,"uid":112185,"like":74,"dislike":0,"score":74,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T13:14:00.000Z","msg":"平時話感建分<br />\n但係你呢件極品係真係要分喎CLS<br />\n<br />\n你講到一啲優點都無，特別係唔太重視你嗰下就收得皮啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋先唔計藍絲係既敵我關係，價值觀，社交圈子先；喺呢啲時勢仲做藍絲既話，一係無良心無人性，一係無腦。佢屋企人係，自稱冷感，其實多數底嗰層都係藍。咁都無將來。"},{"pid":"ef995ff530c197d217d37006dd60032c8a1c2f61","tid":2445221,"uid":70110,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T13:16:23.000Z","msg":"其他唔好講 未結婚都對你咁差<br />\n但你仲諗住同佢一生一世？"},{"pid":"f4149cdf06a7ba82b614c6cc22b2dba7e3de5c50","tid":2445221,"uid":194106,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T13:18:07.000Z","msg":"點解佢對你咁樣仲唔離開？<br />\n唔捨得 習慣咗 定驚搵唔到下一個？"},{"pid":"027ea47034314c179b801e6f4f8e4385cca44692","tid":2445221,"uid":166792,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T13:20:22.000Z","msg":"條友咁垃圾你都唔走 好靚仔定碌鳩識轉灣"},{"pid":"31187402aa54b9f4cb198c30ae9ce2787edcd4f6","tid":2445221,"uid":355346,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T13:21:19.000Z","msg":"點解你每次都咁有心機打咁長嘅膠po<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"998c22c9a6f1b943e74c9d6e62b32e5cd0c33d99","tid":2445221,"uid":59929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T13:21:44.000Z","msg":"咁既藍絲都溝到女<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8267e75aba4679ee0408bb0a4f9fb843ced5fcde","tid":2445221,"uid":168509,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"cited